targets.rawSql:
SELECT "o"."name_translations" as org_name, t.name as team_name, count(distinct("a"."user_id")) as num_users
from "organization" AS "o"
left join "team" AS "t" ON "o"."id" = "t"."organization_id"
left join "association_user_team" AS "a" ON "t"."id" = "a"."team_id"
group by o.name_translations, t.name

select u.full_name, -- a.creator_id as user_id, 
       count(distinct a.id) as num_assets
from asset a
left join "user" u on u.id = a.creator_id
group by u.full_name
order by num_assets desc
